      "url": "https://api.github.com/repos/bitcoin/bitcoin/git/commits/ba2f8af49e1fbe74d46334ec6de477d56b403b06",
      "actor": null,
      "commit_id": null,
      "commit_url": null,
      "created_at": null,
      "html_url": "https://github.com/bitcoin/bitcoin/commit/ba2f8af49e1fbe74d46334ec6de477d56b403b06",
      "tree": {
        "sha": "f3703a1ad0bcbb42b856ccb6d14187121fa1bbca",
        "url": "https://api.github.com/repos/bitcoin/bitcoin/git/trees/f3703a1ad0bcbb42b856ccb6d14187121fa1bbca"
      },
      "verification": {
        "verified": true,
        "reason": "valid",
        "payload": "tree f3703a1ad0bcbb42b856ccb6d14187121fa1bbca\nparent c5f0b684b8ba88c8b27e94581edbaaae2ee5d0a2\nauthor furszy <matiasfurszyfer@protonmail.com> 1775225969 -0400\ncommitter furszy <matiasfurszyfer@protonmail.com> 1775316868 -0400\n\nnet: replace GETBLOCKTXN assert on block read error with graceful shutdown\n\nA failure here indicates a serious inconsistency or disk issue, and the\ncurrent behavior is to abort immediately, which is correct but not the best.\nReplace assert with a fatal error so the node shuts down through the normal\nshutdown path instead.\n\nThis does not change the outcome (the node still stops), but allows a more\ncontrolled teardown, giving other components a chance to flush their state\neven when a particular block (or the blocks dir) on disk is unreachable.\nE.g. the blocks dir might be the only affected, the mempool might be ok,\nand we don't want to lose such information.\n",
        "signature": "-----BEGIN PGP SIGNATURE-----\n\niQIzBAABCAAdFiEEA++0fqwRHQpmlZfQXdI8zGhqpiMFAmnRL4QACgkQXdI8zGhq\npiPAoxAAtrWnpY180Sc/T80hrYei+kHfjPPsmCCW6pN43PUklXSBSl31rBHjj1Qq\n9kwPVcarXclSr4ORsZCV944aJuxyBlE3+6iPKnPtVUzv8Q3FnaSE3sAb9+lhIr/A\n6pqYEro/+7K+rZ+cuw2M+JKG05dCimikgguHgnk/VSlHfA5ysY8cHP8+ahvqJpyA\nh9SmlizwFQwRcAYUTspqvYwPYU3/f7PyClywiurC53/MLSsXeiS3SenImCWgPg1N\n/CCf7LwtXGbqiJygY1lixTvm+K6fcosfg6WxniogfYz1KoEcmIfIp80Chi8UvCEX\n33LkpmPzijfSSRZtyPT5/gtk0FuQHfcV66o36qUufD2yEVxuyJ5IaJ6mAu1D9nIq\nVl8dVMbLU5eKIAa/iJpLam4LWQsIxg2Hp2c1+AdJmOBT/d6p2rZQLB7TxF47Cu3M\nBDrtVkH7YaNNKV2E4WAdd5Bmft7OXdhWaNFBrEx+rapUnc+DHc9vmHVqJwkdhxhC\n+i/oWmp4d5t2i4yTpEikiQJcuMyeaiXoUOsIcUNQgjDftl61cWrsig6FEg7n9+DN\n7WGxRWHNQOhtgJalfU21XGuwatCD1/if96gew1tr11cna5yK9dQy+VtM1Xo6u/Wb\nbnZ+NZxKsWGDYtpLFRVN+75OM3Yt7diCRcDiiH8yNZIbOYgRCK0=\n=Njym\n-----END PGP SIGNATURE-----"
